    <summary>A cross-platform CLI tool that generates ASCII art using Unicode block characters</summary>
    <description>
Blocklet is a modern ASCII art generator that uses Unicode block characters to create beautiful text art. 

Unlike traditional tools like figlet, Blocklet uses solid blocks and box-drawing characters for a more polished look.

## Features
- Beautiful Unicode block-based ASCII art
- Drop shadows with box-drawing characters
- Proper typographic descenders
- Multi-line support
- Automatic word wrapping
- Cross-platform compatibility
- Zero runtime dependencies
